messages.message: It looks like there were some path changes in 20.04 that some of our images are sensitive to. I’ll make sure these get resolved quickly, some of them may take a day or two (I found one where a library isn’t available, if we can’t provide the library I will expose a stopgap base image with 18.04 for that service and others like it)

Impacted services:
```third-party-redis
ocr-service
mount-tservice
refiner-tservice
search-tservice
celery-image-tasks
repo-tservice
account-tservice
docops-service
ocr-emerson```
